        <title>Climate Neutral Companies</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[RobOK]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Wow… that is a huge question, right?</p>
<ul>
<li>at the Individual level, we have to encourage each other to make personal choices and share awareness. I am not always making the best choices</li>
<li>at the community level, sponsor initiatives that are more energy efficient (community solar, electric vehicles, etc.)</li>
<li>at the local and national political level, support organizations that promote conservation</li>
<li>at the national level, probably most important, dismantle the two political parties and rework the system (multi choice voting, less prohibitive rules, etc.)</li>
</ul>
<p>How’[s that to start?</p>
